<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>MacMenuBar.com (中文)</title><link>https://macmenubar.com</link><description>一个包含1400多个Mac菜单栏应用的精选目录</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 11:56:41 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>小重映射</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/tiny-remap/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/tiny-remap.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="Tiny Remap" height="350" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/tiny-remap.webp" width="325"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tiny Remap 让您几乎可以立即在全系统范围内重新映射任何按键，帮助作家、开发者和多语言用户创建更高效、更舒适的打字体验，无需复杂设置。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://egi.ch/en/tiny-remap/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 11:56:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>弹回帽</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/snapback/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/snapback.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="Snapback" height="225" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/snapback.webp" width="375"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Snapback 可帮助您保存和恢复完整的工作区布局，让您轻松返回所需的精确设置。支持窗口对齐、多显示器、键盘快捷键以及快速工作区切换。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://snapbackapp.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 09:55:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>酒吧词典</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/bardict/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/bardict.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="BarDict" height="595" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/bardict.webp" width="400"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BarDict 让词典查询变得快速流畅，它结合了多词典搜索、精致的动画、触控板手势以及以键盘为主的导航方式。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/TokinoyuushaLink/BarDict" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 14:57:00 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>我能有快捷方式</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/icanhazshortcut/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/iCanHazShortcut.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="iCanHazShortcut" height="246" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/iCanHazShortcut.webp" width="450"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;iCanHazShortcut 将终端命令设置为快捷键，将重复性任务转变为快速反应，而非每日微小的烦恼仪式。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/deseven/iCanHazShortcut" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 19:21:48 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>叶子</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/leaf/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/leaf.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="Leaf" height="499" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/leaf.webp" width="500"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leaf 静默监控着在后台浪费内存的非活跃应用，并在适合退出时提醒你。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://satwiktungala.com/apps" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="blank"&gt;访问&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/C2VFDiDCjCk?si=r2juLhS8aaDeno2t" rel="noopener"&gt;观看&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 08:10:25 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>